  "2026-07-13T22:03:31.210Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-13: pm-mi2x supplies generic scale fixtures and pm-atfm evaluates context quality,but no item owns typed-graph property,replay,migration,adapter-parity,and reconstruction conformance across those fixtures."
  "2026-07-14T09:43:38.102Z",codex-gpt5,"Implementation start 2026-07-14: add replay, snapshot, adversarial topology, deterministic analytics, and token-bound conformance coverage for the broad graph SDK bundle; all tests remain sandbox-safe."
  "2026-07-14T10:02:22.642Z",codex-gpt5,"TDD evidence: focused relationship suites pass 21 tests. New relationship history, analytics, and context modules plus the precedence additions report literal 100% statements/branches/functions/lines in focused V8 coverage; static quality, docstring, audit-boundary, and token-budget gates pass."
  "2026-07-14T10:19:34.994Z",codex-gpt5,"Verification evidence: focused relationship suite 21/21 passed; pnpm lint, typecheck, docs/skills, contracts, static quality, audit, and secrets gates passed; full all-source coverage is statements 36575/36575, branches 26252/26252, functions 7405/7405, lines 35721/35721 across 287 files / 5,678 tests. Packed npx smoke passed, package-first dogfood passed 88 real commands, and a fresh pnpm-installed tarball exercised custom ownership, relationship replay, critical-path analytics, and bounded context through @unbrained/pm-cli/sdk. Release gates fail only at live Sentry PM-CLI-29, owned by open pm-7n5a; telemetry is healthy at 0.29% error rate with zero missing error codes."
  "2026-07-14T10:48:29.783Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #556 review round 1 verification: every Gemini/Greptile inline finding was reacted to, answered, and resolved; CodeRabbit/Sourcery rate limits and Codecov success were acknowledged. Focused SDK suite passes 23/23; full suite passes 287 files / 5,680 tests with statements 36,592/36,592, branches 26,271/26,271, functions 7,411/7,411, lines 35,735/35,735. Lint, typecheck, static/docstring 100%, package boundary, token budget, and zero-clone gates pass."
  "2026-07-14T11:06:16.983Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #556 review round 2 verification: six new Gemini/Greptile findings were up-voted, individually answered, tested, and resolved. Full repository gate passes 287 files / 5,680 tests with statements 36,607/36,607, branches 26,286/26,286, functions 7,412/7,412, lines 35,749/35,749; lint, zero-clone, typecheck, static/docstring, package boundary, and token gates pass."
  "2026-07-14T12:58:59.688Z",codex-root,"Conformance progress: focused 44-test graph/relevance suite passes; first literal all-source run passed 287 files/5686 tests and identified only newly introduced edge branches, which now have real malformed timestamp, invalid bound, default-bound, cursor, summary, concurrent persistence, remove replay, corrupt JSONL, sequence drift, and filesystem-error coverage."
  "2026-07-14T13:07:53.656Z",codex-root,"Verification evidence: focused SDK/CLI tests, typecheck, ESLint, jscpd zero clones, 100% docstring/static quality, package-boundary and token-budget gates pass. Full coverage completed 287 files / 5,687 tests at exact 100% across all four metrics; packed-artifact CLI and SDK acceptance proof passed in a clean temporary consumer with zero npm audit vulnerabilities."
  "2026-07-14T13:16:52.868Z",codex-root,"Final release-gate evidence: contracts, docs links, secrets, packed npx smoke, 88-command package-first dogfood, build/typecheck/static quality, exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, version sync, and npm packaging all passed. Live telemetry is healthy at 0.3% finish errors with zero missing error-code rows. The aggregate gate stops only on two unrelated handled Sentry highs: existing PM-CLI-29 tracked by pm-7n5a and new PM-CLI-2B tracked open as pm-d4ns after all-status duplicate checks."
  "2026-07-14T13:17:46.276Z",codex-root,"This implementation tranche adds real concurrent durable-store, replay-corruption, path-containment, cursor, bounds, summary, relevance-parity, CLI-contract, full coverage, package-first, and installed-artifact conformance. The canonical matrix remains open for property generators, thousands-agent/failure injection, migration/federation, golden shell projections, and 10k/100k/million performance envelopes."
  "2026-07-14T14:02:03.088Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #559 review verification: all five first-round inline findings are addressed with behavioral regressions. Focused SDK/CLI tests, typecheck, lint, duplication, docstring, package-boundary, and token gates pass; full repository suite passes 287 files/5689 tests at exact 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines; freshly packed npm consumer passes durable cross-instance refresh and npm audit reports zero vulnerabilities."
  "2026-07-14T14:37:41.469Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #559 round 2 verification: 33 focused tests, typecheck, ESLint, zero clones, 100% docstrings/static quality, package boundary, token gate, and full 287-file/5689-test exact 100/100/100/100 coverage pass. Fresh packed SDK consumer and npm audit pass. Hosted Windows regression had one unrelated existing scale-workspace stdout timing failure while 834 tests passed; the review-fix push will rerun it before any unrelated code change."
  "2026-07-14T15:13:08.640Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #559 round 3 verification: final Windows rerun passed. Defensive decoded-reference, read-lock, fresh-root, and symlink-containment changes pass 33 focused tests, typecheck, strict static quality, full 287-file/5689-test exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, freshly packed installed-package execution, and zero-vulnerability npm audit."
  "2026-07-14T15:30:09.233Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #559 final verification: initial-open lock fix passes 20 focused tests; full suite passes 287 files/5689 tests at exact 100% statements 36813/36813, branches 26416/26416, functions 7432/7432, and lines 35928/35928; fresh packed consumer passes with zero npm vulnerabilities."
  "2026-07-14T15:54:37.620Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #559 round 5 verification: added generic cursor snapshot-envelope validation plus a real two-store durable continuation regression. Full repository coverage passes 287 files / 5,690 tests at exact 100% statements 36,819/36,819, branches 26,434/26,434, functions 7,432/7,432, and lines 35,934/35,934. Typecheck, ESLint, zero clones, 100% docstrings/static quality, package boundary, and token gates pass."
  "2026-07-14T16:24:55.270Z",codex-gpt5,"PR #559 security regression evidence: added post-open symlink replacement acceptance across all durable public I/O methods. Full repository coverage passes 287 files / 5,691 tests at exact 100% statements 36,830/36,830, branches 26,434/26,434, functions 7,433/7,433, and lines 35,945/35,945; focused tests, typecheck, ESLint, zero clones, docstring/static quality, package boundary, token gates, fresh packed install, and npm audit pass."
  "2026-07-21T20:41:58.989Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"Implementation start 2026-07-21: actively build batch atomicity, replay equivalence, resumability, custom-kind, concurrency, and scale regressions for the pm-ju83 backfill surface. The task is worked alongside its canonical blocker so this tranche advances both without creating a duplicate item."
  "2026-07-21T20:55:28.919Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"Conformance progress: focused migration plus existing durable history suites pass 31 tests; the new scale fixture plans and atomically publishes 10,000 edges and replays the exact snapshot without mocks or repository tracker access."
  "2026-07-21T21:15:18.470Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"Scale/conformance evidence 2026-07-21: the tracker-linked 10,000-edge test passed against real filesystem locking and atomic JSONL publication; full repository coverage passed 6,076 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines. The packed public SDK consumer separately proved deterministic planning, atomic publication, and idempotent resume through the installed artifact."
  "2026-07-21T21:37:37.000Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"PR evidence: conformance, concurrency, failure-atomicity, resume, and real 10,000-edge coverage are under review in https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/639."
  "2026-07-21T21:43:57.440Z",codex-relationship-backfill-20260721,"Exact-head review closeout: PR #639 head a3ffacfb is fully green with no unresolved or actionable review findings. This matrix returns open for its remaining property/federation/million-item envelopes."
  "2026-07-22T20:57:34.466Z",codex-graph-platform-20260722,"Implementation start 2026-07-22: actively build reusable adapter conformance, deterministic adversarial/property cases, portable round-trip proof, and an explicit million-node sparse-graph envelope without touching the real tracker."
  "2026-07-22T21:13:32.019Z",codex-graph-platform-20260722,"Verification note: focused adapter coverage reached exact 100/100/100/100 and the real million-node sparse acceptance passed. The first full-suite aggregate attempt ran concurrently with a duplicate invocation and Vitest reported its coverage/.tmp directory removed after the test files passed; this is an execution collision, not a product failure. Rerunning one isolated full coverage process for authoritative evidence."
  "2026-07-22T21:20:57.462Z",codex-graph-platform-20260722,"Property/conformance expansion: deterministic 96-case topology sweep proves content fingerprints and canonical nodes/edges are invariant to source iteration order; the million-node executable now has real entrypoint/report tests so the global 100% gate includes it without exclusions."
  "2026-07-22T21:28:06.054Z",codex-graph-platform-20260722,"Installed-package evidence: a clean temporary npm project installed the packed @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.7.22 artifact, strictly typechecked an external JSON adapter, passed all 7 public conformance cases, federated a custom directed owns ontology, round-tripped the portable snapshot, and reported zero npm vulnerabilities."
  "2026-07-22T21:38:24.126Z",codex-graph-platform-20260722,"PR evidence: the completed property/federation/million-node matrix tranche is under hosted review in https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/648 at commit c98ca0d8."
